    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><br>The Ultimate TTRPG 3D Map-Making Tool</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity with <strong>Master Of Realms</strong>, the revolutionary 3D Smart Hex Map Making Tool designed for tabletop RPG enthusiasts! Dive into immersive worldbuilding and craft <strong>world maps, regional maps, and city or town maps</strong> with ease. Master Of Realms lets you create stunning hex-based maps effortlessly, and you can bring them to life with <strong>3D printing</strong>, <strong>2D export for beautiful paper maps</strong>, or <strong>VTT export for your favorite online platforms</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/80eaec6f81db2a9b022dd76274bd0ec3.poster.avif?t=1772147571\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/80eaec6f81db2a9b022dd76274bd0ec3.webm?t=1772147571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/80eaec6f81db2a9b022dd76274bd0ec3.mp4?t=1772147571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>1. 2D Export:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring your creations to life on virtual tabletops! Export maps in <strong>2D formats</strong> like JPG, PNG, or VTT, with full support for <strong>FoundryVTT</strong> and other platforms. Customize your grid overlay in <strong>Hex or Square</strong> style to match your campaign needs.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/3f62fad21ac394040821c105130b3741.poster.avif?t=1772147571\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/3f62fad21ac394040821c105130b3741.webm?t=1772147571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/3f62fad21ac394040821c105130b3741.mp4?t=1772147571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2. 3D Export:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go beyond the map—bring your realms to life in stunning 3D! Export fully detailed <strong>STL files</strong> for immersive gameplay, epic <strong>3D prints</strong>, or jaw-dropping displays that showcase your world like never before.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/daf829815ee44061b6c47cdcdbfc3df2.poster.avif?t=1772147571\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/daf829815ee44061b6c47cdcdbfc3df2.webm?t=1772147571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/daf829815ee44061b6c47cdcdbfc3df2.mp4?t=1772147571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3. Customize your tiles:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master of Realms gives you full flexibility to bring your imagination to life. Craft custom tiles from scratch, add objects of any shape, size, or style, and place them exactly where you want to create a world that’s truly your own.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/18d091691aa84baf5d889cc5fb6c0b8c.poster.avif?t=1772147571\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/18d091691aa84baf5d889cc5fb6c0b8c.webm?t=1772147571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/18d091691aa84baf5d889cc5fb6c0b8c.mp4?t=1772147571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4. Character Tokens:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into your world through your heroes’ eyes! Master of Realms introduces <strong>Character Tokens</strong> that let you explore your maps and scenes from a character’s point of view. Scale your tokens up or down to match any setting—perfect for tactical encounters or immersive storytelling. Plus, bring your characters to life in the real world with <strong>3D-printable tokens</strong>, fully compatible with the 3D export system for STL files.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/74a3cc060767f868b1182167e0ac07d7.poster.avif?t=1772147571\" width=800 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/74a3cc060767f868b1182167e0ac07d7.webm?t=1772147571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295940/extras/74a3cc060767f868b1182167e0ac07d7.mp4?t=1772147571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Note: Master Of Realms is currently in active development. Features are continuously being implemented and optimized.)</p>",
